data.description: BOM with new price! This beautiful 3-bedroom 2 bath brick home is located in sought after Baker School district and is on the Baker bus route. It is close to shopping, great dining options and the theater. The interior features a spacious great room that is open to the kitchen and breakfast bar, it has 10 ft ceilings and a gas burning corner fireplace. Just off the great room you will find a large sunroom/bonus room that could also be used for an office, playroom, or the perfect place for pets! It leads to the fenced back yard where you have a patio and swing, ideal for entertaining. The large primary suite features pretty chair rail, two walk in closets, a jetted tub and separate shower. The split bedroom plan has 2 guest rooms, guest bath and is convenient to the utility room The breakfast room boast a pretty Bay window and is open to the kitchen. All kitchen appliances including the refrigerator to remain. This precious home has recently had much of the interior painted, fresh carpet in one guest bedroom and all the sinks and faucets have been replace/updated!  It also has gas outlets for the stove, dryer, fireplace and patio. It has a two-car garage as well as a circular drive, great for guest parking. It is USDA eligible according to website, buyer to verify.
